00:59:58,233 --> 00:59:59,773
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi begini rasanya,</font>

929
01:00:00,333 --> 01:00:02,344
<font color=#FFFF00>Menyiram air pada penyihir...</font>

930
01:00:02,344 --> 01:00:04,074
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang selingkuh dengan suamiku</font>

931
01:00:04,444 --> 01:00:05,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa...</font>

932
01:00:06,313 --> 01:00:09,014
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

933
01:00:09,114 --> 01:00:11,413
<font color=#FFFF00>- Apa-apaan...
- Diam, duduklah.</font>

934
01:00:11,744 --> 01:00:12,753
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah</font>

935
01:00:13,813 --> 01:00:16,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat baik padamu</font>

936
01:00:16,054 --> 01:00:18,654
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau menusukku dari belakang seperti ini?</font>

937
01:00:19,523 --> 01:00:23,224
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku rasa pasti ada kesalahpahaman</font>

938
01:00:23,224 --> 01:00:24,623
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita bicara diluar</font>

939
01:00:24,623 --> 01:00:27,994
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, baiklah, mari kita lakukan dengan baik,</font>

940
01:00:28,134 --> 01:00:29,833
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan bicara di luar,</font>

941
01:00:29,964 --> 01:00:31,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan kita lihat...</font>

942
01:00:31,563 --> 01:00:33,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai salah satu kita mati, mengerti?</font>

943
01:00:33,773 --> 01:00:34,904
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari kau</font>

944
01:00:34,904 --> 01:00:36,844
<font color=#FFFF00>Nyonya!</font>

945
01:00:37,043 --> 01:00:38,904
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kumohon, lepaskan!
- Keluar!</font>

946
01:00:38,944 --> 01:00:40,214
<font color=#FFFF00>- Benarkan?
- Nyonya</font>

947
01:00:40,373 --> 01:00:41,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu</font>

948
01:00:42,643 --> 01:00:44,214
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau berbicara pada...</font>

949
01:00:44,643 --> 01:00:45,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Nyonya</font>

950
01:00:45,884 --> 01:00:47,214
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong lepaskan...</font>

951
01:00:47,214 --> 01:00:49,154
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan apa? Kemari kau</font>

952
01:00:49,154 --> 01:00:51,453
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan apa? Kau bilang kau mau keluar</font>

953
01:00:51,453 --> 01:00:52,494
<font color=#FFFF00>Sakit</font>

954
01:00:52,494 --> 01:00:53,494
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo kita keluar</font>

955
01:00:53,494 --> 01:00:54,994
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu salah paham</font>

956
01:00:54,994 --> 01:00:56,994
<font color=#FFFF00>Salah paham apa? Keluar</font>

957
01:01:06,904 --> 01:01:09,244
<font color=#FFFF00>- Keluarlah!
- Ini salah paham.</font>

958
01:01:09,244 --> 01:01:10,773
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu sebentar</font>

959
01:01:10,944 --> 01:01:12,514
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang kau lakukan semuanya bohong</font>

960
01:01:12,514 --> 01:01:14,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana aku bisa percaya padamu?</font>

961
01:01:14,313 --> 01:01:17,043
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Kau pergi ke hotel dengan pacarmu?</font>

962
01:01:17,043 --> 01:01:19,284
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau putus bulan lalu, aku mencari tahu</font>

963
01:01:19,284 --> 01:01:20,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau berbohong?</font>

964
01:01:20,714 --> 01:01:23,884
<font color=#FFFF00>Nyonya bukan begitu, tolong dengarkan...</font>

965
01:01:23,884 --> 01:01:25,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau...</font>

966
01:01:25,054 --> 01:01:27,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Berusaha mencuri suamiku?</font>

967
01:01:28,953 --> 01:01:31,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Sakit!</font>

968
01:01:31,094 --> 01:01:32,194
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong lepaskan!</font>

969
01:01:32,194 --> 01:01:34,464
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan!</font>

970
01:01:37,404 --> 01:01:45,404
<font color=#FFFF00>(Penutup)</font>

971
01:02:03,994 --> 01:02:06,563
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini menyebalkan sekali</font>

972
01:02:36,694 --> 01:02:39,833
<font color=#FFFF00>(Pemain sirkus)</font>

973
01:02:40,293 --> 01:02:42,063
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak membuat ide,</font>

974
01:02:42,063 --> 01:02:43,364
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengumpulkannya</font>

975
01:02:43,364 --> 01:02:45,563
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu karena dia tidak punya asisten</font>

976
01:02:45,563 --> 01:02:48,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak pernah sekalipun melihat dia sebagai pria</font>

977
01:02:48,634 --> 01:02:50,143
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bersalah.</font>

978
01:02:50,143 --> 01:02:51,674
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku harus berhenti?</font>

979
01:02:51,674 --> 01:02:54,114
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku diperlakukan seperti ini?</font>

980
01:02:54,114 --> 01:02:56,884
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang kulakukan hanyalah bekerja keras dan melakukan apa yang diperintahkan padaku</font>

981
01:02:57,844 --> 01:02:59,483
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak mati</font>

982
01:03:00,753 --> 01:03:02,453
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau..</font>

983
01:03:02,453 --> 01:03:05,123
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak mencari pekerjaan?</font>

984
01:03:05,353 --> 01:03:08,424
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada tempat yang tidak terlalu banyak menuntut</font>

985
01:03:09,063 --> 01:03:12,634
<font color=#FFFF00>- Cari seseorang yang dibencinya.
- Apa?</font>

986
01:03:12,634 --> 01:03:13,733
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa...</font>

987
01:03:13,733 --> 01:03:16,634
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang asisten ditugaskan tanpa persetujuan dari wakil presdir?</font>

988
01:03:18,663 --> 01:03:19,873
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mau mencurimu darinya</font>

989
01:03:19,873 --> 01:03:22,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau sudah bertemu dengan tuan Nam?</font>

